long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Rate any website and see other people's ratings

Tired of tutorials that don't work, recipes rating sites that require you to sign up, or missing a dislike button on YouTube? RateTheSite includes a rating scale for all websites using a single RateTheSite account and amalgamates ratings across our user base.

RateTheSIte reviews also include top keyword reviews submitted by other users; keywords may include "outdated" for tutorial blog posts, "violent" to warn others of graphic content, or "fast and easy" for delicious microwavable recipe websites.
